UADataType.Description: Technical Status of the system, that represents the aggregated status of all hierarchical lower systems. This allows to have a top level information on the status of the system which can be drilled down if the system is in any other state than Ok.
Indicates when the equipment requests a replacement. The decision to act on this indication is up to the operator, in accordance with the equipment manual.
Indicates the general operation status of the controller
Indicates the current status of the cooling fan
Indicates the temperature status of the CPU
Indicates the health status of the CPU
Indicates the load status of the CPU
Indicates the type of the latest reset (The reason for the reset).
